<p><strong><img src="images/blog/2.jpg" border="0" alt="" width="789" height="364" /></strong></p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>SAMSUNG GALAXY STAR PRO S7262 (MIDNIGHT BLACK) PRICE: RS.6799</strong></p>
<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Dual Standby SIM (GSM + GSM)</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Android (Jelly Bean) OS</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Wi-Fi Enabled</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">2 MP Primary Camera</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Expandable Storage Capacity of 32 GB</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">4-inch TFT Touchscreen</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">1 GHz Cortex-A5 Processor</span></li>
</ul>
